  "title": "Cleaning Supervisor needed Islandwide",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Supervises and guide the cleaners assigned to an area.</li>\n  <li>Follows-up with work instructions given by the Executive related to the cleanliness of an area.</li>\n  <li>Ensures all cleaning are safely, properly and systematically carried out meeting the cleaning requirements.</li>\n  <li>Supervises daily and monthly planned periodic works allocated to an area.</li>\n  <li>Reports in a timely manner all defects, cleaners attendance and completion of all duties assigned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1. Manage assigned team(s) of Cleaners to maintain cleanliness of assigned area.<br>\n2. Report attendance of Cleaners to site AA and Manager<br>\n3. Meet client KPIs for the day<br>\n4. Brief Cleaners on itinerary of areas to be cleaned for the day<br>\n5. Brief and remind Cleaners on safety procedures before the team proceeds to work for each day<br>\n6. Ensure that Cleaners are carrying the required cleaning tools, and that the tools are functional before travelling to assigned area<br>\n7. Ensure that Cleaners carry out their duties in a safe manner<br>\n8. Instruct Cleaners on more efficient cleaning techniques as and when possible<br>\n9. Praise Cleaners when they exhibit behaviour which is desirable for other Cleaners to imitate<br>\n10. Offer counsel and discipline for errant Cleaners (E.g. Poor attendance, lateness, negative attitudes)<br>\n11. Update Manager on issues and ways to improve cleaning processes</p>",
